{"tid":829935,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網傳馬雲轉移走1200億元 阿里巴巴闢謠：惡意誹謗已報案！","createTime":"2018-09-20T23:50:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T09:29:30.000Z","uid":66943,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ba6a65f6d0a90de68854fbc03e26409b49361959","tid":829935,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T23:50:51.000Z","msg":"今天上午，阿里巴巴官方微博發文，稱連續幾日一篇名為《阿里員工透露：馬總早移走1200億人民幣！網友：不愧是老師》的文章被有組織的進行惡意傳播。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/075005_de144865bb4a2e8981373a38770c926a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F075005_de144865bb4a2e8981373a38770c926a.jpg&h=4f533784&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n　阿里巴巴表示，該文完全捏造事實，惡意誹謗，混淆視聽，移花接木，聳人聽聞，阿里巴巴已經對此向警方報案。<br />\n<br />\n　　在網絡上，《阿里員工透露：馬總早移走1200億人民幣！》文章表示，馬雲2016年將自己持有的阿里巴巴公司3500萬股股票，價值169億美元約1200億人民幣，全部捐給自己在新加坡建立的基金。 <br />\n<br />\n　　現在阿里巴巴官方進行了闢謠說明，並向警方報案處理。<br />\n<br />\n　　在2018夏季達沃斯上的採訪中，馬雲稱他最近也從朋友那裡聽到了&ldquo;自己轉移1200億人民幣&rdquo;的謠言，表示&ldquo;需要學會在口水中游泳&rdquo;。"},{"pid":"46db87ded60265b63e53f73997316ffa6f6f4664","tid":829935,"uid":25858,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T23:53:50.000Z","msg":"肯定唔止咁少<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/04.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87ce083a29fa3d84a97b39e6dceef52e978becd5","tid":829935,"uid":76776,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T23:56:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"308160f12c7984f961aff98d60e6429f93193803","tid":829935,"uid":97240,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T23:58:48.000Z","msg":"馬雲驚到瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba8bbfaba129ea6931d1c5f9d6e4fc3b18d5586","tid":829935,"uid":61280,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T23:59:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-larg